<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Greenview</h2>
    <div>
        <p class="par-lg">With its rolling hill slopes, idyllic landscapes and high elevation, the Greenview community in North West Calgary offers some of the most brilliant views of the surrounding panorama. </p>
        <p class="par-xl">Given its prime location with respect to ease of access to public transportation, schools, recreational venues and other amenities, the community in Greenview is popular among both homebuyers as well as real estate investors. </p>
        <p class="par-lg">The highly active community association of the neighborhood features a bunch of interesting leisure activities and also organizes various social events such as craft fairs and dances from time to time.</p>
    </div>
</div>